The paper presents a tool for type-directed synthesis of bidirectional string transformers, which involves navigating a vast program search space efficiently. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Programming Languages (cs.PL), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Databases (cs.DB) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions using empirical evaluation and a rich equivalence relation on types, which could also place it in the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
